Hi <%= @signup_request.user_con_profile.name_without_nickname %>, the <%= @signup_request.target_run.event.convention.name %> staff have accepted your request to sign up for
<%= @signup_request.target_run.event.title %>.
<% if @signup_request.result_signup.state == 'confirmed' -%>
  <% bucket = @signup_request.target_run.event.registration_policy.bucket_with_key(@signup_request.result_signup.bucket_key) -%>
  You are now signed up in the <%= bucket.name %> bucket.
<% elsif @signup_request.result_signup.state == 'waitlisted' -%>
  Because the event was full, you have been placed on the waitlist.
<% end -%>
